data.description: Constructed in 2015, this expansive residence boasts four bedrooms and four bathrooms within its 2,248 square feet, all set on a generous 8,750 square-foot lot. With granite tile flooring throughout the main areas and cozy carpeting in the bedrooms, it offers low-maintenance syn-lawn in the backyard, perfect for a serene retreat in a tranquil neighborhood. Experience the modern convenience of a next-generation bedroom and living area. The open floor plan kitchen seamlessly integrates with the living room, facilitating easy interaction and entertaining. The split floor plan ensures privacy and functionality, providing ample space for a growing or multi-generational family to thrive.
